Aster Introduces Active Staking Model, asBNB Staking Can Earn Yield, Collateralize Transactions, and Participate in MiningAster, a decentralized trading platform, has announced that the staking strategy for asBNB has been upgraded from traditional "passive income" to "active participation." Users can enjoy the following features after minting asBNB:
1: Earn up to 30% APR in BNB ecosystem rewards by holding;
2: Use as trading collateral for Aster Pro;
3: Earn funding rate收益 while hedging BNB holdings.
Aster stated that asBNB's multi-use model as a staking asset improves staking efficiency and flexibility. [Odaily]
